</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1167661409386">
<problem id="fs-id1167659010599">
<para id="fs-id1167661655797">Which of the following does not occur during the lag period of the primary antibody response?</para>
<list id="fs-id1167659265675" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>activation of helper T cells</item>
<item>class switching to IgG</item>
<item>presentation of antigen with MHC II</item>
